      <akn:section eId="sec_47_1811_04">
        <akn:num>47-1811.04</akn:num>
        <akn:heading>Bases — Determination of depreciation deduction.</akn:heading>
<akn:subsection eId="subsec_47-1811_04_1">
      <akn:num>(1)</akn:num>
      <akn:content><akn:p>The amount of the special depreciation allowance under section 168(k) of the Internal Revenue Code of 1986 [26 U.S.C. § 168(k)]; and</akn:p></akn:content>
    </akn:subsection><akn:subsection eId="subsec_47-1811_04_2">
      <akn:num>(2)</akn:num>
      <akn:content><akn:p>The amount of the cost of property elected to be treated as chargeable to capital account under section 179 of the Internal Revenue Code of 1986 [26 U.S.C. § 179] in excess of the lesser of $25,000 ($40,000 in the case of a Qualified High Technology Company) or the actual cost of such property.</akn:p></akn:content>
    </akn:subsection>
      </akn:section>
